06:09:01.955 --> 06:09:08.395
besides the want of arrangement in the original and of connection among the numerous paragraphs the corruption of the text the

06:09:08.395 --> 06:09:15.715
obscurity of the language and the style and sometimes perhaps the confusion the writers own ideas besides all this there is occasionally an apparent

06:09:15.715 --> 06:09:22.735
Contradiction in the Emperor's thoughts as if his principles were sometimes unsettled as if doubt sometimes clouded his mind a

06:09:23.315 --> 06:09:25.895
Man who leads a life of tranquility and reflection

06:09:25.895 --> 06:09:32.735
Who was not disturbed at home and metals not with the affairs of the world may keep his mind at ease and his thoughts in?

06:09:32.875 --> 06:09:33.655
one even course

