06:10:32.835 --> 06:10:36.315
He lived as frugally and as temperately as the poorest philosopher

06:10:37.175 --> 06:10:43.275
Epictetus wanted little and it seems that he always had the little that he wanted and he was content with it as he has been

06:10:43.275 --> 06:10:44.655
with his servile station

06:10:44.655 --> 06:10:49.455
