06:11:26.775 --> 06:11:30.375
The best and bravest men have moments of doubt and of weakness

06:11:30.375 --> 06:11:37.675
But if they are the best and the bravest they rise again from their depression by recurring to first principles as Antoninus does

06:11:37.675 --> 06:11:41.995
The Emperor says that life is smoke a vapor and st

06:11:41.995 --> 06:11:48.495
James and his epistle is of the same mind that the world is full of envious jealous malignant people and a man might well be

